  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rope it to The Cow!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet Rope Cow – a fearless bovine on a quest for freedom. With a trusty rope in hoof, swing across epic landscapes in pursuit of liberation. Feel like a ninja using your grappling rope to sort obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501800/extras/ade1cea70e66b11f1769f80a012dcf32.avif?t=1749249760\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501800/extras_big/ade1cea70e66b11f1769f80a012dcf32.avif?t=1749249760 width=800 height=116 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURING...</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive single-player story mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Objective-driven game mode with two intense stages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic rope physics for smooth, satisfying swings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A heart-thumping sense of accomplishment with every successful stunt</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ROPE COW</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a game that combines thrilling rope physics and a fresh twist on the classic quest for freedom. Will you help our hero break free, or find yourself wondering: Are we cow… or are we swinger?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Stay safe. Be a happy cow.</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rope it to The Cow!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet Rope Cow – a fearless bovine on a quest for freedom. With a trusty rope in hoof, swing across epic landscapes in pursuit of liberation. Feel like a ninja using your grappling rope to sort obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501800/extras/ade1cea70e66b11f1769f80a012dcf32.avif?t=1749249760\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501800/extras_big/ade1cea70e66b11f1769f80a012dcf32.avif?t=1749249760 width=800 height=116 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURING...</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive single-player story mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Objective-driven game mode with two intense stages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic rope physics for smooth, satisfying swings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A heart-thumping sense of accomplishment with every successful stunt</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ROPE COW</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a game that combines thrilling rope physics and a fresh twist on the classic quest for freedom. Will you help our hero break free, or find yourself wondering: Are we cow… or are we swinger?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Stay safe. Be a happy cow.</i></p>",
